Package eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.wrappers

Class ResponseWrapper

java.lang.Object
eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.wrappers.ResponseWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AssetCategoryResponsesWrapper, AssetCategoryResponseWrapper, KvAttributeResponseWrapper, LocationResponseWrapper, ParameterResponseWrapper, ParameterValueResponseWrapper, SystemResponsesWrapper, SystemResponseWrapper, VendorResponsesWrapper, VendorResponseWrapper
public class ResponseWrapper extends Object implements Serializable
This class wraps the responses travelling from the persistence layer back to the API for a more complete reporting of problems / unsuccessful requests.
Since:
version 0.3.0
Author:
Angela-Maria Despotopoulou [Athens, Greece]
